      <h2 id="submarine-cables">Submarine Cables Landing in France</h2>
      <p>France is the most connected country in Europe for submarine cables, with over 50 cables linking its shores to the rest of the world. Marseille is the main Mediterranean hub, landing point for 15 cables connecting Asia to Europe.</p>
